partnerDetails.about:
Auckland electricians based in Swanson and servicing Auckland. 

Our fast, friendly certified electricians have over 20 years’ experience.

All our workmanship is backed by a 10-year guarantee and we use the best quality materials. Rest easy knowing you’re getting the very best service at a great price with our master electricians.
